2F798A;--shiki-dark:#4C9A91\">  0</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B56959;--shiki-dark:#C98A7D\"> rom</span></span></code></pre>\n<div class=\"line-numbers\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"counter-reset:line-number 0\"><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div></div></div><p>看到没，我的系统盘也就是 <code v-pre>/</code> 根目录存储在 <code v-pre>sde</code> 磁盘下的 <code v-pre>sde3</code> 分区中，我这里需要挂载四个设备 <code v-pre>sda、sdb、sdc、sdd</code>，他们目前都没有挂载点。根据我们之前的理论，<code v-pre>Linux</code> 下一切皆文件，因此一个磁盘肯定对应一个文件。</p>\n<div class=\"language-shell line-numbers-mode\" data-highlighter=\"shiki\" data-ext=\"shell\" style=\"--shiki-light:#393a34;--shiki-dark:#dbd7caee;--shiki-light-bg:#ffffff;--shiki-dark-bg:#121212\"><pre class=\"shiki shiki-themes vitesse-light vitesse-dark vp-code\" v-pre=\"\"><code class=\"language-shell\"><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#A0ADA0;--shiki-dark:#758575DD\"># 找到磁盘的对应文件</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#59873A;--shiki-dark:#80A665\">$</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B56959;--shiki-dark:#C9